# Period-job integrity contract (see tools/period_reconcile/).
#
# Instead of a single monthly fire (which supercronic silently skips if the
# container is down at that minute), reconcile hourly toward the invariant
# "a usage report exists for every closed month". The boot-time reconcile in
# deploy/entrypoint.sh covers downtime that spans whole hourly ticks.
#
# Absolute paths only: supercronic does not inherit the shell PATH.
# reconcile.sh holds the single shared invocation (also used at boot by
# entrypoint.sh), so the two call sites cannot drift.
17 * * * * /app/reconcile.sh
